{"tid":2209110,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[多圖] 夏日性感小熱褲，車房野外露出","createTime":"2020-09-19T11:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T12:28:26.000Z","uid":46678,"like":24,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"89311be6a50f36b010047ce172a37ec425c9c6af","tid":2209110,"uid":46678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T11:47:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pvdgZX1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpvdgZX1.jpg&h=d9a0d604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n早前警方以士巴拿是「攻擊性武器」拘捕一名新巴司機，引發社會譁然，令人憂慮攜帶「搵食工具」有被捕風險。資深驗樓師詹濟南指，今年曾有年輕同事攜帶驗樓工具遭警方截查，幾經解釋才獲放行。他憂慮警方執法標準不清，例如檢測牆身的響鼓錘形似伸縮棍，有時都是放入背囊，自己已經不敢攜帶雷射筆去驗樓，「秀才遇着兵，有理說不清。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/MT6QOZKLIRHYBFOMIOZVYRTQHU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=photo_post\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FMT6QOZKLIRHYBFOMIOZVYRTQHU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=c2f32ffa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200919%2FMT6QOZKLIRHYBFOMIOZVYRTQHU%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dphoto_post&h=a33216a1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200919/MT6QOZKLIRHYBFOMIOZVYRTQHU/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=faceb